  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wings of Redemption is rogue-lite top-down action game with focus on combining melee and ranged combat. Destroy hordes of monsters in randomly generated maps with variety of customizable weapons on your way towards freedom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/48018eb6d6250b56482c2cd6f97140f5.poster.avif?t=1728940006\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/48018eb6d6250b56482c2cd6f97140f5.webm?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/48018eb6d6250b56482c2cd6f97140f5.mp4?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 realms with different environment and randomly generated maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > weapon consisting of 3 parts (bayonet, rifle & magazine), each part replaceable a upgradeable</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > possibility to level up specific build or to increase weapon part level cheaper by taking anything game offers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > specific combat mechanic - magazine reloaded by melee attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > puzzled shop design for nerds (only at first sight)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > no matter how strong hero is - still chance to die instantly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > with greater power comes more responsibility - beware of your own actions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/6c03cb8a8b96417c17e4558b4fbda49f.poster.avif?t=1728940006\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/6c03cb8a8b96417c17e4558b4fbda49f.webm?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/6c03cb8a8b96417c17e4558b4fbda49f.mp4?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wings of Redemption is rogue-lite top-down action game with focus on combining melee and ranged combat. Destroy hordes of monsters in randomly generated maps with variety of customizable weapons on your way towards freedom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/48018eb6d6250b56482c2cd6f97140f5.poster.avif?t=1728940006\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/48018eb6d6250b56482c2cd6f97140f5.webm?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/48018eb6d6250b56482c2cd6f97140f5.mp4?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 realms with different environment and randomly generated maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > weapon consisting of 3 parts (bayonet, rifle & magazine), each part replaceable a upgradeable</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > possibility to level up specific build or to increase weapon part level cheaper by taking anything game offers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > specific combat mechanic - magazine reloaded by melee attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > puzzled shop design for nerds (only at first sight)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > no matter how strong hero is - still chance to die instantly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > with greater power comes more responsibility - beware of your own actions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/6c03cb8a8b96417c17e4558b4fbda49f.poster.avif?t=1728940006\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/6c03cb8a8b96417c17e4558b4fbda49f.webm?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517330/extras/6c03cb8a8b96417c17e4558b4fbda49f.mp4?t=1728940006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
